title: [Moonsedge, Ash and Scarlet]
description: Mountain ash trees lean over the roadside, heavy with clusters of bright red berries.  They shadow the wreckage of a cleric's shop set back from the street, protected from prying eyes by high hedges.  Heavy doors of elm bear the scars of axe blows and the windows are shattered, but a barricade on the other side blocks entry.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
